Branch’s Subprocessors
The list below identifies vendors currently authorized by Branch to process personal data on Branch's behalf where Branch is providing services to customers as their processor, service provider, or equivalent under applicable privacy law(s). Branch will update the vendors listed on this page as appropriate, and will further provide any contractually-required additional notifications to customers.
