Privacy Policy
, which is available at
https://legal.branch.io/#branchio-privacypolicy
(collectively, “Terms”) govern your use of any Site that links to these Terms. Your use of the products and services that are made available online by Branch are governed by a separate agreement.
By clicking “Agree,” accessing, using, or otherwise logging into the Site you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree to these Terms, do not access or use this Site. Branch may modify these Terms at any time at its sole discretion, and as indicated by the “Effective Date” referenced above. By continuing to use or login to the Site after these Terms have changed, you agree to the revised Terms.
