You agree not to access or use the Site in any manner that violates any applicable law, regulation, or any industry guidelines or practices applicable to you or your use of the Site. Failure to comply with these restrictions may result in termination of your access to the Site pursuant to section 10 “Termination” within these Terms.
Whether on behalf of yourself or on behalf of any third party, you agree not to:
