User database management
This type of service allows the Owner to build user profiles by starting from an email address, a personal name, or other information that the User provides to this Application, as well as to track User activities through analytics features. This Personal Data may also be matched with publicly available information about the User (such as social networks' profiles) and used to build private profiles that the Owner can display and use for improving this Application.
Some of these services may also enable the sending of timed messages to the User, such as emails based on specific actions performed on this Application.
Merge Multiple Accounts
We are committed to protecting the personal data you provide to us.  Accordingly, if you have several user accounts and some user accounts are barely used, we will suspend the user accounts are barely used for the purpose of preventing your accounts been accessed without your knowledge.
We'll combine your wallet、Voucher、Rewards、Pat Points in one place. Your asset in the suspended accounts will be transferred to the kept account. This is to ensure that your benefits continue uninterrupted.
Please note you can also decide to recover your suspended accounts. If you want to recover a suspended account or delete an account you no longer want to use, please contact us at
service@patpat.com.
.
Click to agree to the privacy policy to agree to the account merger, click to reject the privacy policy to reject the account merger.
